{"tid":1979024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老愛国湯家驊同志：大陸法原則不無道理","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T07:50:16.000Z","uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41539ffaec3ee66a48aa27f81d55ae80db1dd511","tid":1979024,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"港大法律學院教授、名譽資深大律師陳文敏認為，由《基本法》22條的字面和特區政府以往提交立法會的文件都反映，中聯辦是根據《基本法》22條在港設立的中央機構，不明白為何能豁免於「不得干預」的限制，認為中聯辦解釋強詞奪理。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員兼資深大律師湯家驊認為，基本法的最終解釋權在人大常委會，用大陸法原則理解基本法的話，中聯辦的講法不無道理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521456-20200419.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521456-20200419.htm&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=00a040f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521456-20200419.htm&h=3617e895\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521456-20200419.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f61ab8a699f6d84372c00f615da3a29c09435621","tid":1979024,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8f229b10d9fcb1aaa47c97cbab5c6a28d575e0f","tid":1979024,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"大陸衰十一係咪唔洗拉"},{"pid":"345c18723e29f0b5b9f0813cd1c58b6d6233fdcf","tid":1979024,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ff8315b614c592f1b4421543f5ccbc8e9bd6496","tid":1979024,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"十一哥既加速主義會唔會太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連普通法都想拆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac36e5be2941c05d2e9fa92e3b2199ea51ec8038","tid":1979024,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s